/#
 Defines treatment of non-cash dividends.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.NonCashDividendTreatmentEnum {
    # The treatment of any non-cash dividend shall be determined in accordance with the Potential Adjustment Event provisions.
    PotentialAdjustmentEvent 
    # Any non-cash dividend shall be treated as a Declared Cash Equivalent Dividend.
    CashEquivalent 

}

PotentialAdjustmentEvent.Doc: The treatment of any non-cash dividend shall be determined in accordance with the Potential Adjustment Event provisions.
PotentialAdjustmentEvent.Name: PotentialAdjustmentEvent

CashEquivalent.Doc: Any non-cash dividend shall be treated as a Declared Cash Equivalent Dividend.
CashEquivalent.Name: CashEquivalent
